\x931028.</span> <span class="nowrap">[<a class="int-reflink" href="/pmc/articles/PMC2408531/">PMC free article</a>]</span> [<a href="/pubmed/16284180" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2671596&amp;issue-id=178185&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Science&amp;title=Structure+of+a+V3-containing+HIV-1+gp120+core.&amp;author=CC+Huang&amp;author=M+Tang&amp;author=MY+Zhang&amp;author=S+Majeed&amp;author=E+Montabana&amp;volume=310&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;pages=1025-1028&amp;pmid=16284180&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2671596&amp;issue-id=178185&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="ppat.1000418-Chan1">56. <span class="element-citation">Chan DC, Fass D, Berger JM, Kim PS. Core structure of gp41 from the HIV envelope glycoprotein. <span><span class="ref-journal">Cell. </span>1997;<span class="ref-vol">89</span>:263\xe2\x80\x93273.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/9108481" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2671596&amp;issue-id=178185&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Cell&amp;title=Core+structure+of+gp41+from+the+HIV+envelope+glycoprotein.&amp;author=DC+Chan&amp;author=D+Fass&amp;author=JM+Berger&amp;author=PS+Kim&amp;volume=89&amp;publication_year=1997&amp;pages=263-273&amp;pmid=9108481&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2671596&amp;issue-id=178185&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="ppat.1000418-Li1">57. <span class="element-c